parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: making the vehicle difficult to steer
especially when turning or driving in rainy conditions. The vehicle may also experience a loss of power steering fluid
leading to a loud whining or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion can cause the vehicle to lose power steering, making it difficult to steer, and increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: causing a loud whining or grinding noise
and a loss of power steering fluid. The vehicle may also experience a leak in the power steering system
leading to a loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly, or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: indicating a problem with the airbag system. The airbags may deploy unexpectedly
or not deploy at all in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential issue with the airbag system, which can lead to accidents or injuries if the airbags do not deploy properly in a crash.
symptoms: the airbag light comes on and off
the airbags do not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power lift gate can cause injuries or accidents, especially when occupants are trying to access the rear of the vehicle.
symptoms: The power lift gate does not stay open

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause a range of safety issues, including loss of control, loss of lighting, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete failure of headlights

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sliding Door Lock and Unlock Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning sliding door locks can prevent occupants from exiting the vehicle in an emergency, increasing the risk of injury or accident.
symptoms: Automatic door locks fail to lock or unlock
or doors may not open or close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition and starting issues can cause inconvenience, delay, or even accidents, especially if the vehicle stalls while in motion.
symptoms: intermittent or complete failure of the ignition system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failures can increase the risk of accidents, especially if the vehicle is unable to stop in time.
